title: Toshiwasure Guda Guda Order 2016

synonyms: Fate/Grand Order Farewell to 2016 - Guda Guda Order
Fate/Grand Order Toshiwasure Guda Guda Order 2016
alternative_titles.ja: 年忘れぐだぐだオーダー2016

synopsis:
Oda Nobunaga will join the fight for "GUDAGUDA Honnouji" that suddenly appears at Chaldea! This event features an original story written by none other than the one with a super confusing pen name, Keikenti-san! Of course, the scenario was (basically not) supervised by Kinoko Nasu!

(Source: Fate/Grand Order Wiki)
